{
  "texts": [
    "The computations performed at inference directly generate the ultimate outputs at issue.Directness plays a special role among the features CCC tracks: it modulates the extent to which other features matter for creatorship.",
    "Take developers: without their efforts in building GenAI systems, most users would not be able to produce the images they do.",
    "But developers do not make direct contributions to the creation of specific images.",
    "Rather, their contributions primarily consist in building GenAI systems that have the capacity to produce images.",
    "This is an important achievement but not to be conflated with the production of specific images, to which developers usually contribute only in an indirect, enabling way."
  ]
}